# Anwa environment

# Anthropic API key, read server-side only, never exposed to the client.
# ONE key powers all of Anwa's live AI:
#   - The Guide      : full guided tours generated and translated into any language
#   - Ask the Sky    : the companion chat that plans nights and answers questions
#   - Your keepsake  : the short personalised story on the keepsake card
# Without a key the app still runs everywhere: the Guide serves a committed sample
# tour, the companion gives a real computed answer, and the keepsake uses a
# templated story. Spoken tours and the map need no key at all.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com  then paste it below.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Model used for all of the above. Leave as is unless you have a reason to change it.
ANWA_GUIDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8

# Local SQLite database. The seed script writes here. No external DB needed.
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"
